Libby Villari https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libby_Villari 0 Margaret Elizabeth "Libby" Villari (née Webb; born November 17, 1951) is an American actress. She is best known for her recurring role as Mayor Lucy Rodell on Friday Night Lights. Her film appearances include Infamous, What's Eating Gilbert Grape, Boys Don't Cry, and The Faculty.
